snippet.title: Taiko no Tatsujin World Championship 2024 Malaysia Preliminaries - Emma | Player: Qila (DONkeylah) 🥈
snippet.description:
The Taiko no Tatsujin World Championship 2024 Malaysia Preliminaries is here in Malaysian arcade locations.

The three of us participated in the preliminaries in Aeon Molly Fantasy in Aeon Mall Shah Alam.

The song in the preliminaries is "Emma". Extreme difficulty 7-star. Due to the sensor problem on 1P, the right side DON can't be hit.

Player: Qila (DONkeylah)

Taiko no Tatsujin: Donder! World Championship 2024
太鼓の達人 ドンだー！世界一決定戦2024
